etting around to far-flung city places (like the zoo) wasn't a problem for us. However, the hotel was located near many bus lines so I imagine you could get to where you needed to go if you were traveling without your own vehicle. It's really hard to believe the Chelsea Motor Inn is classified as a budget hotel. We will definitely stay there again.	
